51. VIRTUAL THREADS
============================================================

Virtual Threads Java 21 me final feature ke roop me available hain.

Traditional platform threads operating-system threads se closely mapped hote hain.

Virtual threads JVM-managed lightweight threads hain.


Useful especially for:

- Large numbers of blocking I/O tasks
- Network calls
- Database calls
- Request-per-task style server workloads


Important:

Virtual threads CPU-intensive work ko magically faster nahi banate.

Inka major benefit large-scale blocking/concurrent workloads me hai.


