52. CREATE VIRTUAL THREAD
============================================================

Java 21:


Thread virtualThread =

        Thread.startVirtualThread(() -> {

            System.out.println(
                    Thread.currentThread()
            );

        });


virtualThread.join();


============================================================
53. VIRTUAL THREAD BUILDER
============================================================

Example:

Thread thread =

        Thread.ofVirtual()
                .name("My-Virtual-Thread")
